  "detailed_description": "Life After The Living is a FPS Zombie Survival game. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayer Stats tracking, <br />\r\nHealth, <br />\r\nHunger, <br />\r\nThirst, <br />\r\nTiredness, <br />\r\nStamina, <br />\r\nArm Fatigue for Melee Combat, <br />\r\nBasic EXP/Leveling System (Plans To Expand Soon), <br />\r\nSurvival Timer to track days Survived,<br />\r\nWeapon Health,<br />\r\nRepair Benches,<br />\r\nBeds To Sleep,<br />\r\nLock Picking Ability,<br />\r\nThere are several Weapons in game already,<br />\r\nMultiple Zombie Types",
